  "detailed_description": "Ice Fighter is a fun Tower Defense-like game where you protect and grow your campfire, defending it from waves of enemies during the night, and planning your defense during the day.<br><br>After cold and dark enemies bring a bonfire to the brink of burning out, you, a small fire with legs, are deployed as a last resort defense against the threats.<br><br>You have two weapons: A magma-ball launcher and a flamethrower,<br>along with two tools: An axe and a pickaxe.<br><br>Once the day comes, the enemies melt and you're free to explore the cave, in it, you'll need to gather resources like fuel for your flamethrower or gold, which you can use to buy defenses and upgrades, so the enemies don't extinguish the fire when the sun sets.<br><br><br>Melt enemies with your flamethrower, or shoot them with fireballs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/d0b40c8da1a056c133cf3000b565edb2.poster.avif?t=1720819497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/d0b40c8da1a056c133cf3000b565edb2.webm?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/d0b40c8da1a056c133cf3000b565edb2.mp4?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the cave for resources.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/66a5dc7c331e1a5a326e3a3f779bae5f.poster.avif?t=1720819497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/66a5dc7c331e1a5a326e3a3f779bae5f.webm?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/66a5dc7c331e1a5a326e3a3f779bae5f.mp4?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Manage upgrades with the gold you got from mining.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/ec664e57a726798a52854998d6b1842a.poster.avif?t=1720819497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/ec664e57a726798a52854998d6b1842a.webm?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/ec664e57a726798a52854998d6b1842a.mp4?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Buy turrets and place them tactically.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/1c9c792ae6a1a1ad4be94beb1e1ee23e.poster.avif?t=1720819497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/1c9c792ae6a1a1ad4be94beb1e1ee23e.webm?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/1c9c792ae6a1a1ad4be94beb1e1ee23e.mp4?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Good luck!",
  "about_the_game": "Ice Fighter is a fun Tower Defense-like game where you protect and grow your campfire, defending it from waves of enemies during the night, and planning your defense during the day.<br><br>After cold and dark enemies bring a bonfire to the brink of burning out, you, a small fire with legs, are deployed as a last resort defense against the threats.<br><br>You have two weapons: A magma-ball launcher and a flamethrower,<br>along with two tools: An axe and a pickaxe.<br><br>Once the day comes, the enemies melt and you're free to explore the cave, in it, you'll need to gather resources like fuel for your flamethrower or gold, which you can use to buy defenses and upgrades, so the enemies don't extinguish the fire when the sun sets.<br><br><br>Melt enemies with your flamethrower, or shoot them with fireballs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/d0b40c8da1a056c133cf3000b565edb2.poster.avif?t=1720819497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/d0b40c8da1a056c133cf3000b565edb2.webm?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/d0b40c8da1a056c133cf3000b565edb2.mp4?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the cave for resources.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/66a5dc7c331e1a5a326e3a3f779bae5f.poster.avif?t=1720819497\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2648300/extras/66a5dc7c331e1a5a326e3a3f779bae5f.webm?t=1720819497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st